name: Women's Dab-N-Out Racerback Tank Top
description:
This tank top is an ode to the delicious and ever-so-famous, In-And-Out Burger, as well as the culture of dabbing that naturally ends with a trip for some Animal Fries...so delicious. 

We only made a small batch of these babies so the sizes are limited in availability. 

Sizes will be limited to start, but If we have enough demand we will start printing them in other sizes. Just shoot us an email at HighlyRefined@gmail.com and we will take pre-orders for the next batch.
